         <ddi:abstract xml:lang="en">The Anaphora Typology project (Utrecht University) is surveying the binding properties of reflexives and reciprocals, referred to collectively as 'local coreference strategies'. This database is focused on reflexives, although some information is also provided on pronouns and reciprocals. It contains glossed example sentences (grammatical or ungrammatical) in a variety of syntactic configurations. A limited number of languages are examined in detail. Only a few languages and properties are currently in the system.</ddi:abstract>
